Package org.cesecore.dbprotection

Class CachedCryptoToken

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cesecore.dbprotection.CachedCryptoToken
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.cesecore.keys.token.CryptoToken
    public class CachedCryptoToken
extends Object
implements org.cesecore.keys.token.CryptoToken
    Wrapper for a CryptoToken that caches references to private and secret keys. Used to speed up database integrity protection, where the key should always be available.
    Version:
    $Id: CachedCryptoToken.java 22596 2016-01-18 14:59:25Z mikekushner $
